1921;;The Offenders;;American;;Fenwick L. Holmes;;Margery Wilson, Percy Helton;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Offenders;;A girl (Wilson) is held at mercy of gang of crooks, her only friend being a "half-wit". A murder is committed and blame shifted to the girl.<br><br>The "half-wit" has seen the murder, but cannot remember. When he is cured, his testimony frees the girl.